{"tid":1592813,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[超緊要!!!!!!!]請大家回歸番主線 警暴只係其中一環!!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-24T19:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T21:06:34.000Z","uid":115136,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"a65cc6977a013f3a4a27fdb24c8496d81a01e41b","tid":1592813,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"6 月 以來<br />\n不分化不割蓆非常成功<br />\n但隨時間推展<br />\n發生的事愈來愈多<br />\n難免失焦<br />\n但都希望大家在做每件事前都要勿忘初心<br />\n<br />\n721 831 811 914 915 甚至今日925 濫捕 多人死亡等等<br />\n固其重要 亦明白手足犧牲被捕 大家都好苦惱好傷心<br />\n<br />\n但要記住每日發生的事都只係成場活動一部分<br />\n成場運動除左警暴之外<br />\n仲有幾樣核心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.社會不公不義 (濫捕, 訴求3,4)<br />\n2.對抗港共 -&gt; 土共侵蝕香港 (929 chinazi 遊行 101 遊行, 訴求5)<br />\n<br />\n兩者都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極需要海外關注而不能忽視!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔應該將層面淨係放在香港<br />\n同溫層要cover 都 7788<br />\n目前應該將發生的事情宣揚開去<br />\n<br />\n例如 cockroach 論 同德國種族清洗無分別<br />\n香港會是下一個新疆<br />\n官警鄉黑鐵一家親<br />\n中聯辦 控制香港<br />\n打壓遊行自由 等等<br />\n<br />\n而警暴只係其中一環<br />\n但每一項都係環環相扣 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地唔可以著重在查案, fake news 之上</span><br />\n應該將重點shift 番去目前我地有能力有把握做的事引起國際關注<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在此 <br />\n我唔係叫大家唔理唔查d 無切實證據事情 eg 被自殺<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好放棄 721 811 831 921 等冤案<br />\n但太focus 落未能有充分證據的事件<br />\n會令大家overlook 左我地手頭上武器<br />\n<br />\n就算我地有美國 甚至聯合國backup <br />\n我地都唔可以咩都唔做攤大手板等結果而咩都唔做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要keep 住民氣</span><br />\n民主道路好漫長<br />\n好累 但都要一齊行落去<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落 <br />\nfocus 番重點好嗎??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"922d8ec7269e2fb3c5b8961badca6d96a070e66b","tid":1592813,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"8c66ebcdeb1b0c8ce949df4a817e1bc85e26763b","tid":1592813,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"一齊推爆一個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足！如果你好想討論/搞大一樣野，可唔可以搵一個最全面嘅post集中去做？<br />\n<br />\n1）唔好不斷同樣嘅topic開post。<br />\neg twitter戰線、尋浮屍真相、支持提堂手足、物資post、小店整合post<br />\n<br />\n2）開post前，用關鍵字睇下有無人開過類似嘅post<br />\n<br />\n3)如果係一啲建議，最好有埋實際內容，令個post唔好流於得一兩句互相附和但無人踏出第一步，無實際功用嘅post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">歡迎自行增加行動整合post/每個topic最熱門/全面嘅post落下面：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1）行動整合post:</span></span></strong></span><br />\n［長期置頂］熱門推爆行動Post詳情、文宣 （善用不推文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <ins>呢個post不斷更新呢個list</ins><br />\n<br />\n[行動] 927 928 929 930 101 (加返太子恐襲悼念日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592450</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2)文宣Post</span></strong></span><br />\n[國恨家仇] 黑警發鼠瘟暴行GIF集合 612-925<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3)聲援手足Post</span></strong></span><br />\n法庭要人聲援！聽日46位手足上庭！43個暴動、1個冇得保釋坐緊啦！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">4）對抗黨鐵post(閘機、跳閘etc)<br />\n[整合] 輕鬆壞閘機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">欠：<br />\n聯署post<br />\n記者會post<br />\netc<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，善用不推文！請幫手完善個list<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cd2ab175712d75f3f7e1e062595d01691cc610","tid":1592813,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"agree 要用普世價值繼續connect 西方<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"98ff7342f44c45cb110d6cdb747d4926ad4d5e0b","tid":1592813,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:17:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>Tg channel 在此 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=68fe556d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> <span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>"},{"pid":"2916ba1b0d5bfb7812ed6bc6eb537a2c80986f53","tid":1592813,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:18:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62cec56e98b759c3d03917a1122c03310dc151cd","tid":1592813,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-siz